meta.description:
Welcome to cliq.social community! 

As a registered user on our decentralized microblogging platform, you can communicate with members of different platforms throughout the fediverse.

By joining the cliq.social community, you accept and agree to the following:

Be respectful. Be friendly. Be welcoming. Be considerate. Be patient. Be careful in the words that you choose.

If you experience or witness unacceptable behavior, please report it by contacting us

meta.name: Jaeger Website
meta.description:
Welcome to Jaeger.Website!
A fediverse social media micro-blogging platform running on "Misskey".
Freespeech *but* don't not post anything illegal. This server is based in Germany.
Other than that I don't enforce any other rules on you. Free speech! Just be sure to tag nsfw accordingly.
Registrations will be open until around 50-100 users.

More information/links about this instance:
- Terms of Service
- Federation Policies
- Server Performance
